if you've bought the gift card from flipkart directly, you can resend the gift card details to the recipient by following these simple steps:
1. go to 'my orders'2. select the gift card order3. click on 'resend gift card' and the recipient will get the gift card with a new pin
if you've got the gift card as a gift, you may get in touch with the original buyer and they will be able to help you out.
